The paper proposes a new approach to positive-unlabeled (PU) learning in the context of deep learning. The paper is likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with a learning problem. Additionally, the proposed approach involves labeling data, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of deep networks, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
